cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.HC

This paper deals with the application of machine learning techniques to detect and classify cognitive distortions in mental health text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of AI techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category. The paper also deals with mental health, which makes cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) possible categories.
